* **CSS Transforms:** [MDN Web Docs - CSS Transforms](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/transform)
* **Understanding CSS Pseudo-classes:** [Various tutorials available on the web - search "CSS pseudo-classes"]

